{"tid":2157330,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Samsung電話於最近更新後被系統強制安裝了一些電話程式。","createTime":"2020-08-15T03:22:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T04:45:05.000Z","uid":73092,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d70513b18802b8f48505689b332eb585ef6fb0d6","tid":2157330,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T03:22:48.000Z","msg":"【讀者投稿-手機安全】<br />\n<br />\n有讀者的Samsung電話於最近更新後被系統強制安裝了一些電話程式。<br />\n<br />\n事主昨日觀看影片時，突然彈出一個問題，問是否繼續攝錄，問題下面有兩個選擇，一邊是「取消」，另一邊就是「繼續」。而係事主並無開過任何攝錄鏡頭下，又自動按了三次取消。其後發現系統強制下載了很多電話程式，即使還原原廠設定也無法刪除，懷疑更新之後已被監控 。<br />\n<br />\n而事主查看這些無法強制刪除的電話程式時，該程式的官方說明以簡體字呈現，並擷除了相關的評論。希望三星手機的使用者多加留意，以免洩漏個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PPPNinternation/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPPPNinternation%2F&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8ckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=8944919d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/PPPNinternation/</a><br />\nIG：<a href=\"https://instagram.com/pppn_international\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fpppn_international&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8ckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=cacab69c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/pppn_international</a><br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"http://t.me/pppnewstg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fpppnewstg&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8ckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=a5024f2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/pppnewstg</a><br />\n#PPPN #以曝制暴 #歡迎投稿"},{"pid":"27b99752c710664c22f18c00d83bb1e189570068","tid":2157330,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T03:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9ea32fdd1e82581a603d737377837a9e5b5314","tid":2157330,"uid":33788,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T03:37:56.000Z","ms